item.title: UVa CS Tea Time
item.description: ©Tango Order Food You may order food and drinks by phone, the Internet or visiting the restaurants/stores in advance. You don’t have to wait until Friday to place the food order. Food delivery service is recommended for saving your time. You are eligible to have a temporary T4 parking permit if the food delivery service is not available and you would have to pick up from the restaurants/stores.

item.title: About CSGSG
item.description: The CSGSG serves as the assembly of all graduate students in the Department of Computer Science at the University of Virginia. All graduate students, Master’s and PhD, within the department of computer science or in the computer engineering program are automatically members of the CSGSG.
